@startuml
title Call It Cure It - Runtime Request and Launch Sequence

skinparam shadowing false
autonumber

actor "User Browser" as Browser
participant "DNS\ncallitcureit.com" as DNS
participant "Edge Caddy\ncallitcureit-edge-caddy\n:80/:443" as Edge
participant "Dev Caddy\ncallitcureit-dev-caddy\ninternal :80" as EnvCaddy
participant "Frontend\ncallitcureit-dev-frontend\nNginx :80" as Frontend
participant "Backend\ncallitcureit-dev-backend\nGo/Fiber :8080" as Backend
database "Dev SQLite Volume\n/app/data/app.db" as DB

== App page request ==

Browser -> DNS : Resolve dev.callitcureit.com
DNS --> Browser : Hetzner IP

Browser -> Edge : GET https://dev.callitcureit.com/scenarios
note right of Edge
Edge Caddy owns public TLS.
It routes only by hostname.
end note

Edge -> EnvCaddy : GET http://callitcureit-dev-caddy/scenarios\nHost: dev.callitcureit.com
note right of EnvCaddy
Environment Caddy is HTTP-only:
http://{$APP_DOMAIN}

It must not force HTTPS.
end note

EnvCaddy -> Frontend : GET /scenarios
Frontend --> EnvCaddy : 200 index.html\nReact SPA fallback
EnvCaddy --> Edge : 200 index.html
Edge --> Browser : 200 index.html

== API request for scenarios ==

Browser -> Edge : GET https://dev.callitcureit.com/api/v1/scenarios
Edge -> EnvCaddy : GET http://callitcureit-dev-caddy/api/v1/scenarios
EnvCaddy -> Backend : GET /api/v1/scenarios
Backend -> DB : SELECT published scenarios
DB --> Backend : rows
Backend --> EnvCaddy : 200 JSON
EnvCaddy --> Edge : 200 JSON
Edge --> Browser : 200 JSON

== Login request ==

Browser -> Edge : POST https://dev.callitcureit.com/api/v1/auth/login
Edge -> EnvCaddy : POST /api/v1/auth/login
EnvCaddy -> Backend : POST /api/v1/auth/login
Backend -> DB : SELECT user by email
DB --> Backend : user/password hash
Backend --> EnvCaddy : 200 token OR 401 invalid credentials
EnvCaddy --> Edge : response
Edge --> Browser : response

== Deployment launch sequence ==

box "Server Launch" #LightYellow
participant "Operator" as Operator
participant "Makefile" as Make
participant "Docker Compose\ncallitcureit-dev" as Compose
end box

Operator -> Make : make server-dev-build
Make -> Compose : docker compose -p callitcureit-dev build
Compose --> Make : backend/frontend images built
Make --> Operator : build complete

Operator -> Make : make server-dev-up
Make -> Compose : docker compose -p callitcureit-dev up -d
Compose -> Backend : start container
Backend -> DB : apply migrations via docker-entrypoint.sh
Backend -> DB : EnsureDevAdmin if DEV_SEED_ADMIN=true
Backend --> Compose : healthcheck OK
Compose -> Frontend : start container
Compose -> EnvCaddy : start container
Compose --> Make : dev stack running
Make --> Operator : server-dev-up complete

Operator -> Make : make edge-up
Make -> Edge : docker compose edge up -d
Edge --> Make : edge running on 80/443
Make --> Operator : edge-up complete

Operator -> Make : make server-dev-smoke
Make -> Edge : curl https://dev.callitcureit.com/api/v1/healthz
Edge -> EnvCaddy : proxy request
EnvCaddy -> Backend : GET /api/v1/healthz
Backend --> EnvCaddy : 200 {"status":"ok"}
EnvCaddy --> Edge : 200
Edge --> Make : 200
Make --> Operator : smoke passed

@enduml